descript.abstract: This point layer contains start and end nodes for all of the street segments in Cambridge. It also contains street names for all intersections.
descript.purpose: Created in accompaniment with the Centerlines data layer. Each street segment has a "from node" and a "to node" to connect the streets and to indicate the direction of the segment.
